# 🔥 XSS (Cross‑Site Scripting)

## ✅ What XSS Is

XSS occurs when **attacker‑supplied input executes JavaScript in the victim’s browser**.

This runs:
✅ With your site’s permissions\
✅ As the logged‑in user

